      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2022R2) is under institutional version control. The ML training pipeline is implemented in a Git-tracked repository with unit tests covering data ingestion, feature scaling, and model serialization. XGBoost 1.7.3 is pinned in the requirements file. SQA level meets MRL 2 requirements."
