      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver passes published benchmark cases for internal rotating flow; ML code verified against reference implementations.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent was verified against the FDA Critical Path benchmark for centrifugal pump flow (FDA-2010-D-0064). The XGBoost training script was verified by reproducing published results on the UCI blood transfusion dataset to within 0.5% of reported AUC, confirming correct library integration."
    },
    {
