      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) < 5% for wall shear stress on impeller blade surfaces.",
      "rationale": "Three mesh refinement levels (2.1 M, 5.8 M, 14.2 M cells) were evaluated. GCI for peak wall shear stress on the impeller blade was 3.2%, satisfying the acceptance criterion. The medium mesh (5.8 M cells) was selected for production CFD runs used to generate the ML training dataset."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
