      "rationale": "Bench tests were conducted at the five nominal operating points (2.5 L/min at 2000 RPM; 3.5 L/min at 2500 RPM; 4.5 L/min at 3000 RPM; 5.5 L/min at 3500 RPM; 6.0 L/min at 4000 RPM) using bovine blood at 37°C, hematocrit 33±2%. Deviations from target flow rates were within ±2.1% and rotational speed within ±0.8%, satisfying the acceptance criterion."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
