      "acceptanceCriteria": "Surrogate-predicted RH agrees with bench-measured RH within 15% at all five nominal operating points.",
      "rationale": "Surrogate predictions of RH ranged from 0.41 to 0.87 across the five operating points. Bench-measured RH ranged from 0.38 to 0.91. Maximum relative deviation was 8.3% at the 6.0 L/min, 4000 RPM condition, within the 15% acceptance threshold. All five predictions satisfied RH < 1."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
